  "keyFeatures": [
    "Create private music-sharing groups with friends",
    "Upload MP3/MP4 audio files to groups",
    "Invite members to groups via email",
    "Download tracks shared within your groups",
    "Dashboard with recently uploaded tracks across all groups",
    "Spotify local file integration support",
    "Authentication via Supabase (email/password)"
